# --- Evidence vs Release Hygiene (Governance) ---
# Ensure evidence directories are traversable
!docs/_evidence/
!docs/_evidence_archived/

# Default: ignore logs everywhere (Release Surface)
*.log
*.out

# Evidence surface: allow logs as auditable artifacts
!docs/_evidence*/**/*.log
!docs/_evidence*/**/*.out
